  "was_decomposed": true,
  "final_sql": "WITH latest_disbursed AS (     SELECT          acnt_code,         MAX(acnt_name) KEEP (DENSE_RANK LAST ORDER BY txn_date) AS acnt_name,         MAX(customer_name) KEEP (DENSE_RANK LAST ORDER BY txn_date) AS customer_name,         MAX(cur_code) KEEP (DENSE_RANK LAST ORDER BY txn_date) AS cur_code,         MAX(adv_date) KEEP (DENSE_RANK LAST ORDER BY txn_date) AS adv_date,         MAX(adv_amount) KEEP (DENSE_RANK LAST ORDER BY txn_date) AS original_adv_amount,         MAX(adv_amount * rate) KEEP (DENSE_RANK LAST ORDER BY txn_date) AS adv_amount_in_mnt     FROM dbm.loan_balance_detail     WHERE adv_amount IS NOT NULL       AND (acnt_name IS NOT NULL OR customer_name IS NOT NULL)     GROUP BY acnt_code     HAVING MAX(adv_amount) KEEP (DENSE_RANK LAST ORDER BY txn_date) > 0 ) SELECT      acnt_code,     acnt_name,     customer_name,     adv_date,     original_adv_amount,     cur_code,     adv_amount_in_mnt FROM latest_disbursed ORDER BY adv_amount_in_mnt DESC FETCH FIRST 1 ROW ONLY;",
  "result_count": 1,
  "final_answer": "Таны хүсэлтийн дагуу Монгол Улсын Хөгжлийн Банкны хамгийн өндөр олголттой зээлийн мэдээллийг хүргэж байна:  - Дансны код: 3600000127 - Дансны нэр: ЭРДЭНЭС ТАВАН ТОЛГОЙ ХК - Харилцагчийн нэр: ЭРДЭНЭС ТАВАНТОЛГОЙ ХК - Олгосон огноо: 2012-10-05 - Олгосон дүн: 100,000,000 ам.доллар - Валют: ам.доллар - Олголтын дүн төгрөгөөр: 359,361,000,000 төгрөг"
